<div class="home">
  <h2><i class="fa fa-tachometer"></i> Dashboard</h2>
  
  <div class = "alert alert-info">
    <h2 style = "margin-top: 0px">
    <i class = "fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Notice</h2>
    <p>Thank you for signing up!</p>
    <p>Here are the CCNs for the course if you are interested in signing up for a unit:
    <p><b>Adjunct Section for Computer Science:</b>
    <ul class="list"><li class="list">COMPSCI 98-152 (CCN 26432)</li>
    <li>COMPSCI 198-152 (CCN 26933)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please choose the section that corresponds to you (upper div or lower div), which corresponds to your class standing. Only one of them will work for you (so if one doesn't work, try the other one).
    <p>Make sure that you have chosen "P/NP" instead of letter grade, and that you select "1 unit" in the variable units section in order to enroll on Telebears.
    <p>Enrolling in a section here guarantees enrollment into our system. If you do not wish to enroll on Telebears, that is fine as well.
    <p><i>We also understand that there is some problems signing up on Telebears at the moment, we are currently working on getting that fixed. Thank you for your patience.</i>
  </div>

  <div class = "switch-sections">
  <% if @enrolls.size > 0%>
    <h3> Your sections</h3> 
    <% @enrolls.each do |enroll| %>
      <% curr_course = Course.find(enroll.course_id) %>
      <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h3 class="panel-title"><i class="fa fa-book"></i> <%= curr_course.course_name %> 
          
          <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-remove'></i>".html_safe, enrollment_path(enroll), :method => :delete, class: "delete-course", data: { confirm: "Are you sure you want to drop #{curr_course.course_name}?"}%>
           
          </h3>

        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <% if not enroll.section_id.nil? %>
            <% curr_section = Section.find(enroll.section_id) %>
            <h4>  <%= link_to curr_section.name, section_path(curr_section) %></h4>
            <%= link_to '<i class="fa fa-exchange"></i> Switch Sections'.html_safe, switch_section_path(enroll), class: "btn btn-warning" %>
            <%= link_to '<i class="fa fa-trash-o"></i> Drop Section'.html_safe, drop_section_path(enroll_id: enroll.id), class: "btn btn-danger" %>
          <% else %>
            <h4>You're not enrolled in a section. </h4> 
            <%= link_to '<i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Add Section'.html_safe, edit_enrollment_path(enroll),  class: "btn btn-success"%>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to '<i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Add Course'.html_safe, new_enrollment_path,   class: "btn btn-success"%>
  <% else %>
  <div class="well">
  <h4>You're not enrolled in any courses. </h4>
  <%= link_to '<i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Add Course'.html_safe, new_enrollment_path,   class: "btn btn-lg btn-success"%>
  </div>
  <% end %>  

  </div>
</div>  
